---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 156
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Interiorization and Transmutation
    of the Faculties
---
Every time you attempt satisfaction of a desire the knowledge comes that it
is better to desist. Repeated reminders of this kind will in due course
weaken the desires.
